OL,3,CWhy dialling 999 doesn't always mean
OL,4,Cgetting an ambulance - explained
OL,6,FDial 999 and you might expect blue
OL,7,Flights and sirens. But increasingly at
OL,8,FSouth Western Ambulance Service NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust, an ambulance won't
OL,10,Fbe coming.
OL,12,FInstead they're offering advice over
OL,13,Fthe phone and via video calls to less
OL,14,Furgent cases.
OL,16,FThe system - called 'Hear and Treat' -
OL,17,Fis the trust's way of trying to spread
OL,18,F450 ambulances around a population of
OL,19,Fup to 23 million people.
