OL,3,CWhy dialling 999 doesn't always mean
OL,4,Cgetting an ambulance - explained
OL,6,FSWASFT's own figures show that in
OL,7,FOctober 2025 for instance, 18.05% of
OL,8,Fcalls were dealt with via the Hear and
OL,9,FTreat system - that's 15,563 cases in
OL,10,Fwhich someone dialled 999 but didn't
OL,11,Fget an ambulance.
OL,13,F"There simply aren't the ambulances
OL,14,Favailable to send to every patient
OL,15,Fthat dials 999", says Jon Knight,
OL,16,FSWAFST's Head of Emergency Operations
OL,17,FCentres.
